---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact | AI‑Native.es"
  description="Two senior partners on every call, zero account managers. Tell us where you want to go – we’ll tell you what it will really take."
>
  <section class="px-6 pb-20 pt-16 md:pt-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center" data-animation="fade-up">
      <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-cyan-300">
        Contact
      </p>
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold md:text-5xl">Let’s talk about your product</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-zinc-400">
        Whether you’re in discovery, scaling, or firefighting mode, we’ll give you an honest view on where we can help
        – and where someone else might be a better fit.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-12 grid max-w-5xl gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.4fr,1fr]">
      <div data-animation="fade-up">
        <ContactForm />
      </div>

      <aside
        class="space-y-4 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-6 text-sm text-zinc-300"
        data-animation="fade-up"
      >
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">What to include</h2>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">
            A few bullet points are enough: what you’re building, where you are today, and what a “win” would look like
            in 12 months.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-zinc-800 pt-4">
          <h2 class="mb-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">Direct email</h2>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">
            Prefer email? Reach us at{' '}
            <a href="mailto:hola@ai-native.es" class="text-cyan-300 hover:text-cyan-200">
              hola@ai-native.es
            </a>
            .
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-zinc-800 pt-4">
          <h2 class="mb-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">Typical clients</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-1 text-xs text-zinc-300">
            <li>• Spanish companies expanding across Europe</li>
            <li>• European teams who want a senior Spanish partner</li>
            <li>• Founders who want to ship something serious from day one</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

